{
  "stem": "2353.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--that I had belonged to for three years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there, too, no anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were all terrific friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had-- I mostly had non-Jewish boyfriends, so it-- it-- it-- it was just unthinkable what happened afterwards.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, oh yes, definitely.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I said, every time there was some bad press in the United States in the papers, I would get a-- a-- a chance to, to compete someplace.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was one incident where, in the New York papers, they wrote about that I was not allowed to compete in the German championships.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the German sports organization was questioned.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why wasn't she allowed?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, she couldn't compete because she doesn't belong to the German Track and Field Association.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But why wasn't I allowed to, to-- you know, I wasn't allowed to be a member because I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they, they, they got around everything in a very sneaky way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as I said, they got-- whatever they wanted to do, they did, whichever way they could get, get to it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So was it to the extent that outside nations were threatening not to come to the Olympics?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Many, many nations.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I think in-- in-- in Madison Square Garden, they had about 20,000 people-- a-- a-- a-- a mass protest, not to send people, not to send the team to, to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And wherever-- there was a lot of propaganda going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Do not send a team to Germany because that discrimination is definitely going on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was, in the archives-- Washington, you know, National Archives-- I have letters here where the ambassador, American ambassador, wrote letters to the State Department what was going on.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I don't think they paid any attention to it whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh no.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
